### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Evidence query — Multi-symbol E2E smoke
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### This file validates the multi-symbol vertical slice:
###   Binance WS → ingest → OBSERVATION_EVENTS → derive → store → gateway HTTP
###
### Scenario: 2 symbols (btcusdt, ethusdt) × 4 timeframes (60s, 300s, 900s, 3600s)
###
### Prerequisites:
###   make up           # starts nats, configctl, gateway, ingest, derive, store
###   make seed-multi   # seeds configctl with btcusdt + ethusdt bindings
###   wait ~90s         # ingest needs to connect WS + derive needs a 60s window
###
### Or use the automated smoke scripts:
###   make smoke            # single symbol (btcusdt)
###   make smoke-multi      # multi-symbol (btcusdt + ethusdt)

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080

### 1. Health check — gateway is alive
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Readiness check — gateway can reach configctl and store
GET {{baseUrl}}/readyz
Accept: application/json

###

### --- BTCUSDT (symbol 1) ---

### 3. Latest 60s candle — btcusdt
### Expected: 200 with candle data (after ~75s) or 200 with null candle (if < 60s)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Latest 300s candle — btcusdt
### Expected: 200 with candle data (after ~6min) or 200 with null candle (if < 300s)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=300
Accept: application/json

###

### 4b. Latest 900s candle — btcusdt (TC-01)
### Expected: 200 with candle data (after ~16min) or 200 with null candle (if < 900s)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=900
Accept: application/json

###

### 4c. Latest 3600s candle — btcusdt (TC-01)
### Expected: 200 with candle data (after ~61min) or 200 with null candle (if < 3600s)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=3600
Accept: application/json

###

### --- ETHUSDT (symbol 2) ---

### 5. Latest 60s candle — ethusdt
### Expected: 200 with candle data (after ~75s) or 200 with null candle (if < 60s)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Latest 300s candle — ethusdt
### Expected: 200 with candle data (after ~6min) or 200 with null candle (if < 300s)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=300
Accept: application/json

###

### 6b. Latest 900s candle — ethusdt (TC-01)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=900
Accept: application/json

###

### 6c. Latest 3600s candle — ethusdt (TC-01)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=3600
Accept: application/json

###

### --- HISTORY queries ---

### 7. Candle history — btcusdt 60s (last 5)
### Expected: 200 with candles array (may be empty if < 2 windows finalized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/history?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&limit=5
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Candle history — btcusdt 300s (last 3)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/history?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=300&limit=3
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Candle history — ethusdt 60s (default limit=10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/history?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### --- RANGE queries (S20) ---

### 10. Range query — btcusdt 60s, last hour
### since/until are unix seconds. Adjust to current time window.
### Example: since = now - 3600, until = now
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/history?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&since=1710000000&until=1710003600&limit=20
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. Range query — since only (open-ended upper bound)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/history?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&since=1710000000&limit=10
Accept: application/json

###

### 12. Range query — until only (open-ended lower bound)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/history?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&until=1710003600&limit=10
Accept: application/json

###

### --- TRADE BURST queries (S23) ---

### 13. Latest trade burst — btcusdt 60s
### Expected: 200 with trade_burst data (after ~75s) or 200 with null (if < 60s)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/tradeburst/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 14. Latest trade burst — btcusdt 300s
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/tradeburst/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=300
Accept: application/json

###

### 15. Latest trade burst — ethusdt 60s
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/tradeburst/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 15b. Latest trade burst — btcusdt 900s (TC-01)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/tradeburst/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=900
Accept: application/json

###

### 15c. Latest trade burst — btcusdt 3600s (TC-01)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/tradeburst/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=3600
Accept: application/json

###

### --- Error handling ---

### 16. Missing params — should return 400 (validation error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt
Accept: application/json

###

### 17. Empty params — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/latest
Accept: application/json

###

### 18. History — invalid limit (> 100) — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/history?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&limit=999
Accept: application/json

###

### 19. History — since after until — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/candles/history?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60&since=1710003600&until=1710000000
Accept: application/json

###
